{"tid":2381942,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"旺角油麻地疫區髒亂 坑渠鼠覓食四竄","createTime":"2021-01-27T03:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T05:15:01.000Z","uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d52c63cf276add7809ed4e9b3e1d02256591550e","tid":2381942,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210127/photo/bkn-20210127032242075-0127_00822_001_01p.jpg?20210127100411\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210127%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210127032242075-0127_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20210127100411&h=b5ca0323&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5b6aa7474807747d272ec78b9069508ea44bf8e","tid":2381942,"uid":132137,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"一早要全部舊區重建"},{"pid":"849b5f0567a83361d4f8bdaf0d35cbb9a8ec2fd8","tid":2381942,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"本港<del>新冠肺炎</del>疫情持續嚴峻，油尖旺區更成為爆疫重災區，東網記者在今日(27日)凌晨在旺角及油麻地區的排檔及街市巡視。至近凌晨3時，記者在旺角深圳街街市乍聽有老鼠的吱吱叫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，未幾目睹有3隻碩大的老鼠，在污水積聚的路邊竄出，其中有老鼠明目張膽，跳上街市檔口近砧板處及發泡膠箱之間亂竄覓食，毫不怕人。<br />\n而在油麻地新填地街及北海街交界的排檔及街市，在一間店舖門外，有4至5隻老鼠在坑渠口竄出，牠們看似十分熟路，聯群結隊逕自走向該店外路邊，嚙咬遺留在路面的米飯殘渣，有老鼠更毫不浪費，飽餐之後，還叼走吃剩的飯餸，返回鼠竇慢慢享用，與一眾鼠輩大快朵頤。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而爆疫嚴重的深水埗區，鼠患同樣嚴重，食環署早前在區內後巷，擺放了放置鼠餌的捕鼠器。昨晚(26日)記者在區內巡視，其中在汝州街一處後巷，發現當局放置的7個老鼠籠中，其中有一至兩個籠捉到老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但距離滅鼠成效，相信還言之尚早。<br />\n目前疫情爆發之際，油尖旺及深水埗區內大廈多屬唐樓，內有大量劏房、環境衞生惡劣，多幢大廈出現渠管亂駁及老化問題，不時傳出臭味的後巷更淪為老鼠樂園。有碩大的肥鼠不時在街上亂竄，情況令人側目，事件亦反映食環署滅鼠不力，難為街坊在疫魔下要與鼠患共存，面對新冠肺炎疫情及鼠疫兩疫夾擊。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb75055ecb2665719df11d37caf7ee5e592d595","tid":2381942,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"點解新冠肺炎殺唔到老鼠"},{"pid":"8ab24c4be8397f457aa40e9b4e3de69296ac4cee","tid":2381942,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9fb75055ecb2665719df11d37caf7ee5e592d595","tid":2381942,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"點解新冠肺炎殺唔到老鼠"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:13:29.000Z","msg":"可能已殺唔少"},{"pid":"e3c79c978d59b1842b06806ee4091ba8fcd0b3d7","tid":2381942,"uid":387461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"封區包唔包埋老鼠？<br />\n有老鼠想走佬犯唔犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbe8cdab961e1a287383f40d2c1a15528dd9fda","tid":2381942,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9fb75055ecb2665719df11d37caf7ee5e592d595","tid":2381942,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"點解新冠肺炎殺唔到老鼠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"蛋白結構唔o岩, pick up 唔到條rna"},{"pid":"90be767ea3949314336c692bffda4d4e7f4f3311","tid":2381942,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3c79c978d59b1842b06806ee4091ba8fcd0b3d7","tid":2381942,"uid":387461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"封區包唔包埋老鼠？<br />\n有老鼠想走佬犯唔犯法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee34b39b1987a5de9be84fe8f8ad025398aad8b","tid":2381942,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fb75055ecb2665719df11d37caf7ee5e592d595","tid":2381942,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"點解新冠肺炎殺唔到老鼠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"因為佢地細胞冇ace2 依個鎖"},{"pid":"1f7c228f73458d42efa9a4ace347381d47d990bd","tid":2381942,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,